data.name: JS Cocoa
data.description:
A Dutch cocoa processor with the passionate belief that potentially beautiful cocoa should not be wasted.

We not only help reducing cocoa waste streams by reusing cocoa residues from the cocoa industry while creating more value for our customers, but we generate extra income for our cocoa farmer partners in Africa by buying cocoa bean misfits at origin.

In Ghana, JS COCOA set out to develop a sophisticated and fine-mazed network of farmers and transporters, to collect and trade these specific extraordinary beans to be used in our production process. That’s how the beautiful RESIGHA saw daylight back in 1984 in the heart of Ashanti region, a wholeblood daughter of JS COCOA.

Back in the Netherlands, we produce and deliver high standard cocoa ingredients to customers all over the world. Thanks to the unique combination of experienced specialists on production processes and customer-focused product, along with a flexible supply chain.

data.name: JS
data.description: The unique cocoa powders of JS are highly defatted and near 100% fiber solids. Applied in bakery and confectionery, ice cream and dairy as well as in low caloric health products. Ensuring high intense coloring and dispersibility in liquid is exceptionally good. Due to less fat, a mild alkalization still results in a strong intrinsic color impact without requirements to label alkali (under 7%).

data.name: JS Natural Cocoa Powder - ZERO
data.description: ZERO is the natural fat reduced cocoa powder from Theobroma cocoa that brings a warm red brown color to your product.This highly defatted cocoa powder  (less than 0.5% fat) is the solution for affordable cocoa content in the segments cookie and biscuits, confectionery and bakery products. Especially interesting in lauric fat based compound coatings & fillings to avoid fat blooming and fat incompatibility. ZERO brings intense coloring capabilities, unique solubility in (cold) liquids (making it suitable for foamy applications, dairy and non-dairy beverages), with lower calories and an attractive price.

data.name: JS Refined and Deodorized Cocoa Butter - OLYMPUS USP/NF
data.description: OLYMPUS USP/NF is a double refined cocoa butter. Very low in free fatty acids for sensitive cosmetics, pharmaceutics and personal care products. It has a very smooth, creamy and velvetty structure. It is very clear and clean. The color can be adjusted in line with customer preferences. It is FDA approved and part of USP-NF standards in the U.S. OLYMPUS is the market leading brand in the U.S. for decades.

data.name: JS Dark Alkalized Cocoa Powder - NERO
data.description:
NERO is an alkalized fat reduced cocoa powder from Theobroma cocoa. Less than 0.5% fat.

Fine cocoa powder with improved solubility and intense color darkening effect due to its low fat content.

Perfect to add a hint of dark chocolate color to dry and wet applications. Specially those with fat compatibility issues.

Ideal for chocolate spreads, cremes, foamy applications and dairy and non dairy beverages.

Optimal darkener of chocolate biscuits, cakes, muffins and Oreo type of products.

Due to JS COCOA unique Dutch processing applied at zero fat level, NERO has an enhanced taste without soapy off-flavors when compared to black powders with 10-12 % fat content.
